data.enText: a person, company, etc. that sb owes money to

tr: a person to whom money is owed by a debtor
someone to whom an obligation exists

value.def: Your creditors are the people who you owe money to.

example.ex: The company said it would pay in full all its creditors.
example.tran: 该公司称将偿清所有债权人的债务。
